re expected to react in the same way.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Sep 2018) 4aIliad. 4aZeus. 4adestiny. 4a heroism. 4a myth.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2018 Englishz978311060400908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2018z9783110603095oZDB-23-DGD0 cEPUBz97831106015410 cprintz978311060137440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110602456423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110602456.jpg  a978-3-11-060400-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG  aZDB-23-DGDb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017